channel.title: What inspires you?
channel.description:

I love it, but I have a low attention span and could do with some tips.

item.title: What inspires you?
item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

Runetracker (thanks to mopar telling me about it) since I like to see big xp gains. Highscores (top 55k fuck yeah;3), being better than most people at pvm is pretty important to me tbh lmao, the best stuff in game always keeps me training etc, a lil bit of my showing off, pvp, the variety of things you can do on rs.
Basically, since I’m nowhere near the best at the game I keep trying to get their sorta thing. I’ve always wanted to be one of those players that can do anything PVM and PvP wise amazingly. Once I get their I’ll probably get bored n quit as their wont be a goal to achieve.

Read full topic
